  "title": "🍓 PART-TIME SNACK KIOSK ASSISTANTS @ CENTRAL/NORTHEAST! $12/HR",
  "description": "<p>Looking for a fun part-time role? Join our vibrant snack kiosk team and serve up smiles every day! 😊 <br /></p><h3><strong>📍 Work Locations </strong></h3><p>Chinatown | Ang Mo Kio | Pasir Ris <br /></p><h3><strong>💰 Pay & Benefits </strong></h3><ul><li><p>$12 per hour </p></li><li><p>Public Holidays: Double pay!  <br /></p></li></ul><h3>🗓️ Work Schedule </h3><ul><li><p>5-day work week (between Monday – Sunday) </p></li></ul><p>Shift timings:  </p><p>A: 9:00am – 3:00pm </p><p>B: 11:00am – 5:00pm </p><p>C: 4:30pm – 10:30pm </p><ul><li><p>30h a week, one 6h shift each day! </p></li></ul><h3>🌟<strong> What You’ll Be Doing </strong></h3><ul><li><p>Prepare and pack snacks according to store standards </p></li><li><p>Operate tea-making equipment</p></li><li><p>Take customer orders and handle cash transactions accurately </p></li><li><p>Maintain cleanliness and follow food safety & hygiene regulations </p></li><li><p>Deliver friendly, efficient customer service and handle enquiries professionally <br /></p></li></ul><p>✅ Requirements </p><ul><li><p>WSQ Food & Hygiene Certificate </p></li><li><p>Able to work shifts  <br /></p></li></ul><p>📥 Interested? Apply Now! </p><p>📱 Send your resume to 8032 2021  </p><p>📧 Or email: <a href=\"mailto:admin@crew.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">admin@crew.sg</a> </p><p>*<em>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em> </p><p>Megan Tan </p><p>Outsourcing Team </p><p><strong>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd – CREW by HRnet </strong></p><p>EA License No: 24C2435 </p>",
